: 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Speed_Association\", \"score\": 0.9631474148058248, \"rank\": 0.03824018490968221, \"text\": \"ASA\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Speed_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Speed_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletics South Africa claims to have removed Adams from the Team SA squad due to his inability to prove his fitness.\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2531, \"end\": 2553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletics_South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Athletics South Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletics_South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletics_South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 2597, \"end\": 2599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.092881460615391e-35, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an exclusive letter obtained bySABC Sport, ASA outlined the reasons for Adams's removal from the squad.\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2696, \"end\": 2699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Speed_Association\", \"score\": 0.9631474148058248, \"rank\": 0.03824018490968221, \"text\": \"ASA\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Speed_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Speed_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A reliable source informed the national broadcaster that the figures, including Jean Verster (ASA Track and Field Chairperson), Hendrick Mokganyetsi (ASA Athletes Commission Chairperson), Paul Gorries (relay coach), Perrie Posthumus (Adams 'coach), Hezekiel Sepeng (ASA official), and Adams himself were made aware of the reasons for his removal.\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 3104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2886, \"end\": 2906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hendrick_Mokganyetsi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hendrick Mokganyetsi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hendrick_Mokganyetsi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hendrick_Mokganyetsi\"}, {\"begin\": 2946, \"end\": 2958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Gorries\", \"score\": 0.9999401209049497, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paul Gorries\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Gorries\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Gorries\"}, {\"begin\": 3024, \"end\": 3027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Speed_Association\", \"score\": 0.9631474148058248, \"rank\": 0.03824018490968221, \"text\": \"ASA\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Speed_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Speed_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The letter states, \\\"You did not compete in any local or other competitions during the 2024 season due to injury, and ASA was hopeful that you would recover in time for the national championships.\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3223, \"end\": 3226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Speed_Association\", \"score\": 0.9631474148058248, \"rank\": 0.03824018490968221, \"text\": \"ASA\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Speed_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Speed_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your evaluation as part of the OPEX athlete program was also scheduled for the championships, but unfortunately, you were unable to participate due to your injury.\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3465, \"entities